{"tid":50086,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[字型撚] 老人家整嘅香港字型","createTime":"2016-12-22T07:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T00:53:29.000Z","uid":28759,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20abc8f46186cd967d8f88cbd667eed816cb30d6","tid":50086,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"有班老人家整左套「香港自由楷書」，照住香港教育局嗰套嚟執。<br />\n<br />\n詳情︰ <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20151128/19390468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20151128%2F19390468&d=S4kTmJZgfEkq1OG%2Fkmv%2FJgv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=d90ce0b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20151128%2F19390468&h=a5940df4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20151128/19390468</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Q7xFQah.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQ7xFQah.png&h=2ccc6e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁小弟手痕就喺公司整咗幅對比圖，全部都係同一個 font size<br />\n<br />\n左上係用大陸繁體(GB18030)嘅微軟雅黑<br />\n左下係用台灣繁體嘅微軟正黑<br />\n右上係大家用慣用熟嘅內建標楷體，同時係老人家字型嘅抄考對象<br />\n右下係老人家「開發」嘅「香港自由楷書」<br />\n<br />\n第一行係慣用嘅「永東國酬愛鬱靈鷹袋」<br />\n第二行係早輪 Justfont 用黎 check GB18030 嘅字<br />\n第三、四行係我貪得意加上去嘅<br />\n<br />\n特別留意下戶字頂、草花頭、肉/月字部<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇字型JJ一齊研究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafc30ec09cc5298adb175ce80d14679bacd2ee2","tid":50086,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"香港字幾靚 不如叫iphone加字型"},{"pid":"4f6d835ceb81b868e22e18eec9d6e2b31262321e","tid":50086,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港字幾靚 不如叫iphone加字型</blockquote><br />\n可能我睇厭左標楷體，冇話覺得特別靚<br />\n不過好有細個睇港版書嘅感覺<br />\n呢個「溫」同「麻」嘅寫法好有回憶"},{"pid":"f6f392326b7a00c2b54b9d52effdcb29c7